{
  "stem": "323.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I am very happy that both my children are working for nonprofit organizations, to some extent my son.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because what I actually did in advertising, even though I loved it, it was really absolutely meaningless.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is something I think I also tried to teach my children, that it really didn't mean anything at all and to do something worthwhile, if at all possible, with your life.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but the added piece for me about being in the Jewish community is that I had worked in the nonprofit, nonsectarian sector.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this has an additional meaning for me, because it's for the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even though it's not something in terms of my observance, personally it's meaningful to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I just feel that life is very short, and one should do something where someone else will benefit, which is-- there's certainly no benefit for anyone in advertising except monetary rewards.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But if you could help someone, I think that's a great thing to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is why I have been volunteering, too, now, since I have free time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm doing things to help people when I can.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I work for the Big Apple Greeter, which I love.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I should have been a tour guide, but it's too late for that now.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I have been taking people, basically foreign people, who visit New York City for the first time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I show them Manhattan, because I really love Manhattan.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm also in a senior aide group now, where I have an old person that I visit once a week and spend like an hour, two hours with.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is someone who doesn't have a family and really has no contact with the outside world, except for people like me.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
